    }}><inlineCode parentName="h2">{`diffOfSquares(term1, term2)`}</inlineCode></h2>
    <p>{`In order to implement the difference of squares formula in our code with Mathium, we must call the function using Mathium's API, as such:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-ts"
      }}>{`import * as Mathium from "mathiumjs";

